# Auto-generated wiki insights and append-only logs.
# These are produced by the agents on every cycle and pollute `git status`
# without adding value to the repo. Keep the directory structure (.gitkeep)
# but ignore the contents.
data/wiki/insights/*
!data/wiki/insights/.gitkeep
data/wiki_india/insights/*
!data/wiki_india/insights/.gitkeep
data/wiki/log.md
data/wiki_india/log.md

